Package.Description:
Developer:: ShuraBB

- By pressing the ALT key you can switch between different maps.
- Full support for the functions of the standard minimap (displaying the commands “attention to”, “support by fire”, “need help”, etc.);
- Accurate calculation of the review of the tank (taking into account the installed equipment, consumables, pumpability of the crew and its perks);
- Display of the place of the last exposure of the enemy;
- Customizable range circles (color, transparency, visibility);
- Dynamic circle “tank viewing radius”, calculated taking into account installed additional equipment and pumped crew perks;
- Customizable circle drawing objects;
- Magnification of the minimap in the center of the screen;


Included maps:
- Tactical Maps
- Heat Maps

Additionally added maps:
- HAWG´s Tactical Maps
- HD Maps WOTInspector
- TechMaps WOTInspector
